@startuml
actor Actor
participant "UI: React" as UI
participant "AuthMiddleware" as Auth
participant "MemberController" as Ctrl
participant "MemberService" as Svc
participant "UserRepository" as Repo
database "Database" as DB

Actor -> UI: Completa formulario de invitación
UI -> Auth: POST /api/members/invite (InviteDTO)
Auth -> Auth: Validar Token & Rol (Admin/MemberAdmin)
Auth -> Ctrl: inviteMember(data)
Ctrl -> Svc: inviteMember(data)
Svc -> Repo: findByEmail(data.email)
Repo -> DB: SELECT ...
DB --> Repo: null
Repo --> Svc: UserNotFound
Svc -> Repo: create(new User(status=PENDING_INVITE))
Repo -> DB: INSERT ...
DB --> Repo: User Created
Svc -> Svc: Enviar Email Notificación
Svc --> Ctrl: Invitation Result
Ctrl --> Auth: 201 Created
Auth --> UI: Success Message
UI --> Actor: Muestra confirmación
@enduml
